text: Doguzhiyev () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Yelenovskoye Rural Settlement of Krasnogvardeysky District, Adygea, Russia. The population was 10 as of 2018. There are 4 streets. == Geography == The khutor is located 13 km east from Krasnogvardeyskoye, on the left bank of the Laba River. == References == Category:Rural localities in Krasnogvardeysky District
title: Doguzhiyev
